01:09:42.870 --> 01:09:44.750
- Hi.
- Robin's thinking of moving here.

01:09:44.920 --> 01:09:47.840
Do it. We need more cute babes
in this town.

01:09:48.000 --> 01:09:51.300
Yeah, right. Like there aren't
already four babes to every man.

01:09:51.470 --> 01:09:54.680
- Kim, look who's here.
- Dixon, what are you doing here?

01:09:54.840 --> 01:09:58.350
- Didn't your wife just have a baby?
- I'm celebrating!

01:09:58.520 --> 01:10:00.350
- Yeah, right.
- Dance?

01:10:00.520 --> 01:10:03.230
That's the other problem.
Small town, big chemical company.

01:10:03.390 --> 01:10:05.650
Everybody knows
everything about...

01:10:07.690 --> 01:10:11.820
Whoa, daddy!
Look what just walked in.

01:10:13.530 --> 01:10:17.620
Somebody's gonna hurt someone

01:10:17.780 --> 01:10:19.240
Before the night is through

01:10:19.410 --> 01:10:21.250
Who? The guy
with the black suit?

01:10:21.410 --> 01:10:26.000
Somebody's gonna come undone

