Hang on, Peterson!

01:55:45.300 --> 01:55:46.900
Grab on!

01:56:03.650 --> 01:56:06.320
I got it! I got it.

01:56:07.660 --> 01:56:09.070
Atta girl.

01:56:23.550 --> 01:56:25.550
"As Vargas shouted
his final command...

01:56:25.720 --> 01:56:28.890
the Thin Man's eyes
measured Peterson for a coffin.

01:56:29.050 --> 01:56:32.640
She turned, a breath away from
the barrel of his .22 automatic."

01:56:32.810 --> 01:56:36.180
Poetry, sweetheart.
Absolute poetry!

01:56:36.350 --> 01:56:40.860
Look who's talking. "The cold metal tip
of the pistol brushed against my hair.

01:56:41.020 --> 01:56:44.900
