were empty as two holes in a mask."

01:56:46.570 --> 01:56:49.360
Honey, I got goose bumps!

01:56:49.530 --> 01:56:52.280
You ever think
of writing a novel?

01:56:52.450 --> 01:56:54.540
And give up the newspaper game?
Never.

01:56:57.660 --> 01:56:58.660
Okay!

01:57:02.420 --> 01:57:06.170
