- Male, female reporters solve mystery...

01:57:10.510 --> 01:57:11.760
- fight...
- Mm-hmm.

01:57:11.930 --> 01:57:14.010
Make up, fall in love...

01:57:14.180 --> 01:57:16.480
save the day,
go on a honeymoon.

01:57:16.640 --> 01:57:19.390
Sounds like a best-seller
to me.

01:57:20.900 --> 01:57:23.360
- Darling.
- Yes, my love?

01:57:23.520 --> 01:57:28.240
You didn't really mean it when you said our
scoundrel days were behind us, did you?

01:57:33.330 --> 01:57:36.790
They are for me
if they are for you.

01:57:36.950 --> 01:57:40.120
All right. I promise
to go straight if you do.

01:57:42.000 --> 01:57:43.000
I do.

01:57:46.420 --> 01:57:48.880
Then I do too.

01:57:58.180 --> 01:58:00.140
Brackett, get this!

01:58:00.310 --> 01:58:02.270
- Two guys with .385 coming right
out of that, uh, that bank.

